{
  "texts": [
    "They refined the questions when necessary.",
    "This resulted in TALES-QA, a question bank consisting of 1, 600+ questions, which capture nuanced and diverse cultural knowledge about regions in India.",
    "Question Bank Creation (TALES-QA)Question Generation.",
    "We used the misrepresentation spans identified by our expert annotators to generate questions.Specifically, GPT 4.1 was instructed to formulate a single standalone question given the story text, the annotated span, its categorization and rationale as inputs.",
    "The model was instructed through prompting to ensure that the resulting candidate question directly addressed the contextual inconsistency, was interpretable without access to the original story, and avoided ambiguity."
  ]
}